{"tid":2016493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參議院《武漢病毒追責法案》包括要求釋放所有香港民主人士。","createTime":"2020-05-14T11:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T12:44:34.000Z","uid":294518,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"784357c70435bed04acdc71dbfa5f58a235d7ac5","tid":2016493,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"《武漢病毒追責法案》提出，要求總統在該法通過後60天內獲得中共全面配合，進行國際調查，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同時釋放所有香港民主人士。</span></span></strong>如果60天內沒有獲得中共配合，授權總統制裁中國。<br />\n<br />\n一旦此法案通過，硬碰硬的對抗正式拉開。<br />\n參考文件詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hydesmith.senate.gov/sites/default/files/2020-05/COVID-19%20Accountability%20Act%20-%20Summary.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hydesmith.senate.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2020-05%2FCOVID-19%2520Accountability%2520Act%2520-%2520Summary.pdf&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=a1aa4364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hydesmith.senate.gov/sites/default/files/2020-05/COVID-19%20Accountability%20Act%20-%20Summary.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"67515bd5bb993e57037055af2c57f7f522179004","tid":2016493,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"ba4bafa19d30be8031f3e4e431123c98be30e454","tid":2016493,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"授權總統制裁中國<br />\n<br />\n核彈都要總統撳制"},{"pid":"2d452892472bfa6d7354e1dd47494e203b2a03b9","tid":2016493,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"又吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155a042e2e48a885bacfba2978e1113dd9d544b3","tid":2016493,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:06:53.000Z","msg":"其實係咪即係放晒所有因反送中而俾狗咬嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ea97